{"id": "art-246", "label": "Art. 246", "title": "Art. 246", "slug": "art-246", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 246 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1851216660\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1768\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1851216660\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În termen de 3 luni de la data public&#259;rii\nproiectului de fuziune sau de divizare în una dintre <span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nprev&#259;zute la art. 242, adunarea general&#259; a fiec&#259;rei <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> participante va hot&#259;rî asupra\nfuziunii sau diviz&#259;rii, cu respectarea <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iilor</span>\nprivind convocarea ei.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1578623244\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1767\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1578623244\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazul unei fuziuni prin <span class=SpellE>înfiin&#355;area</span>\nunei noi <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> sau al unei\ndiviz&#259;ri prin <span class=SpellE>înfiin&#355;area</span> unor noi <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>, proiectul de fuziune sau de divizare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259; sunt <span class=SpellE>con&#355;inute</span>\nîntr-un document separat, actul constitutiv sau proiectul de act constitutiv al\nnoii/noilor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> vor fi aprobate de\nc&#259;tre adunarea general&#259; a fiec&#259;reia dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\ncare urmeaz&#259; s&#259; <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> înceteze <span\nclass=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}